CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 23, 1958, pg. B11 reads: "The Cooks Receive - Mr. and Mrs. David Cook Sr., left, entertained Sunday in honor of their son, David Jr., and his bride, the former Evangeline Moore of Whiteville, N.C. Held on the beautiful lawn of Mr. and Mrs. Hubert Smith of Finland St., the reception drew cores of socialites from cosmopolitan Pittsburgh and out of town. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of David Cook, wife Eunice Cook, bride Evangeline Moore Cook, and groom David Cook Jr., posed on lawn of Mr. and Mrs. Hubert Smith, Finland Street, for Moore-Cook wedding reception
